<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這天終於到來了！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還問我什麼事……<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有新的居民搬過來了喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然同伴增加<delay8 />讓人很開心呢，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了讓對方早點適應這座島，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得多幫幫忙才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你已經見過<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新搬來的居民了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很想早點去打聲招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是如果對方還在忙著整理行李之類的，<delay8 />
會不會給人家添麻煩呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，<delay8 />
今天有新居民<delay8 />搬來了吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我得早點去打聲招呼才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經見過今天搬來的人了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我倒是<delay8 />還沒呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種時候<delay8 />第一印象很重要，對吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等我稍微讓自己打起精神之後，<delay8 />
就去見對方吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的<delay8 />生日喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />來說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是一年一度的特別日子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家一起幫<gender3 m="他" f="她" />慶生吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，明天就是<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的生日了！<delay20 />
我問你喔，<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經準備好禮物了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是都準備好了喔！<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是這麼認為啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但對方會不會喜歡我的禮物，<delay8 />
要是不拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />也不知道呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的生日呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就我來說的話，<delay8 />現在我已經不像以前那樣，<delay8 />
會單純因為生日就覺得高興……<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過正是因為如此，<delay8 />大家幫自己慶生的時候，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才讓人打從心裡覺得開心呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="013_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上<delay8 />
就要跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />道別了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會笑著送<gender3 m="他" f="她" />啟程的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />含淚送行，<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />就太不識趣了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
就要離開這座島了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
如果你有話想對<gender3 m="他" f="她" />說，<delay8 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可要趁現在喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛剛<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
在整理行李呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上<delay8 />就要離開這座島了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然天下沒有不散的筵席，<delay8 />
但不管經歷過多少次別離，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />寂寞的心情還是絲毫不變呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>